This paper is primarily focused on data migration, which is a common problem in database systems. Therefore, cs.DB (Database) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new technique that uses Datalog program synthesis, which involves automated reasoning and logical inference, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely sub-category as well. The use of Datalog also falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed technique involves machine learning and statistical analysis, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
